long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Rev up your new tab with the iconic Nissan Skyline! This Chrome extension brings the thrill of this legendary car to your browser.

The Nissan Skyline live wallpaper extension showcases the sleek and powerful design of this classic Japanese sports car. With a clean, user-friendly layout, it offers a smooth browsing experience alongside visually stunning graphics.

Browse the web effortlessly using the Google search bar, organize shortcuts to top sites, and stay informed with a clock-date display.

Key Features:

Live Wallpaper featuring the iconic Nissan Skyline
Google Search Bar for seamless browsing
Customizable site shortcuts for easy access
Clock-Date display to stay on schedule

Feel the power of the Skyline in every new tab! Discover more automotive themes at Gameograf.com to enhance your browser.
